Package: clickme
Maintainer: Nacho Caballero <nachocab@gmail.com>
Author: Nacho Caballero <nachocab@gmail.com>
Version: 0.3.0
License: GPL-3
Title: Straight from R to JS: Create interactive visualizations from R
Description: R has powerful data processing abilities, but it can only generate
    static plots. Browsers allow interactivity but the data they work with is
    often statically defined. Clickme bridges both worlds by making it easy to
    create interactive visualizations using R data.
Imports:
    knitr (>= 1.2),
    yaml (>= 2.1.7),
    stringr,
    rjson
Suggests:
    testthat,
    stringr,
    roxygen2
